e from the mouse-like {{wp|fat-tailed dunnart}}; this marsupial\'s carrot-shaped tail stores nutrition in the form of fat for times of scarcity.\n\n====Name origin====\nAzurill is a combination of \'\'{{wp|Azure (color)|azure}}\'\' (a shade of blue) or \'\'azul\'\' (Spanish and Portuguese for \'\'blue\'\') and \'\'rill\'\' (a small river or brook). Its name may also be derived from its evolutions, Marill and Azumarill.\n\nRuriri may be a corruption of 瑠璃 \'\'ruri\'\' ({{wp|lapis lazuli}}) which is theoretically in {{p|Marill}}\'s—its evolution—name, or it may be a variation of {{wp|azurite}} (a blue rock).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Normal|type2=Fairy\n|ja=ルリリ \'\'Ruriri\'\'|jameaning=From 瑠璃 \'\'ruri\'\' (lapis lazuli), with the last syllable repeated\n|fr=Azurill|frmeaning=Same as English name\n|es=Azurill|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Azurill|demeaning=Same as English name\n|it=Azurill|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=루리리 \'\'Ruriri\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of its Japanese name\n|zh_cmn=露力麗 / 露力丽 \'\'Lùlìlì\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Transliteration of its Japanese name. Also contains {{tt|露 \'\'lù\'\'|dew}}\n|hi=अजुरील \'\'Azurill\'\'|himeaning=Transliteration of English name\n}}\n{{left clear}}\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Misty\'s Azurill]]\n* [[Partner Pokémon (Mystery Dungeon)]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Normal|type2=Fairy}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Normal|prevnum=297|prev=Hariyama|nextnum=299|next=Nosepass}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Baby Pokémon]]\n[[Category:Mystery Dungeon starters|298]]\n[[Category:Pokémon with cross-generational evolutions]]\n[[Category:Pokémon that evolve by friendship]]\n[[Category:Single-type Pokémon|298]]<!--In Gens III-V-->\n[[Category:Pokémon that have had their type changed]]\n[[Category:Pokémon that appeared in the anime before their game debut]]\n\n[[de:Azurill]]\n[[es:Azurill]]\n[[fr:Azurill]]\n[[it:Azurill]]\n[[ja:ルリリ]]\n[[zh:露力丽]]'}